<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('partial/head.ejs') %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partial/header.ejs') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
      <h1 class="text-center py-4 h1">About My Blog</h1>

      <!-- Blog Description -->
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p class="lead text-center">
            Welcome to our blog! This platform is designed to share knowledge,
            insights, and news about the latest trends in web development,
            technology, and beyond. Whether you're a seasoned developer or just
            starting out, we aim to provide valuable content that educates,
            informs, and inspires.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Mission Section -->
      <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <h2 class="text-center h2">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-center">
            Our mission is simple: to empower developers and tech enthusiasts
            with the information they need to excel in their careers. Through
            tutorials, industry updates, and personal stories, we hope to foster
            a community of lifelong learners and innovators.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Meet the Creator Section -->
      <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <h2 class="text-center h2">Meet the Developer</h2>
          <div class="text-center">
            <!-- <img
              src="https://via.placeholder.com/150"
              alt="Creator"
              class="rounded-circle mb-3"
            /> -->
          </div>
          <p class="text-center">
            Hi, I'm Tarek Mostafa, a passionate web developer with a strong
            background in sales, customer service, and retail. After spending
            over 19 years in various industries, I decided to dive into web
            development to combine my passion for technology with my experience.
            This blog is my way of giving back to the community by sharing
            knowledge and helping others in their learning journey.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Technologies Used Section -->
      <div class="row justify-content-center mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-8">
          <h2 class="text-center h2">Technologies We Use</h2>
          <p class="text-center">
            Our blog is built using the latest technologies to ensure a seamless
            and modern experience for our users:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush text-center">
            <li class="list-group-item">
              Node.js & Express.js - Server-side framework
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              EJS - Templating engine for dynamic content
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              PostgreSQL - Database for managing blog posts
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              Bootstrap (or Tailwind CSS) - Responsive design and styling
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Link Back to Home Page -->
      <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Back to Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer><%- include('partial/footer.ejs') %></footer>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS (optional) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
